Module com.example.finalprojectwithjavafx
Package gameobjects.SaveLoader

Interface Savable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Armor, AttackBottle, Bandit, BareHands, Bat, Clothes, CombatArmor, Consumable, Entity, FaultyMagicRifle, Goblin, healthPotion, Items, Knife, LeatherArmor, LinkTile, MapBase, Murderbot, Mutant, Navigator, Pistol, PlateArmor, Player, RectangularMap, Rifle, Sword, throwingKnife, Tile, TileBase, Weapon, Zombie
    public interface Savable
    Interface for classes which can be saved to a text file. Classes that implement this interface need a corresponding loader class. The corresponding loader class extends SaveLoader.

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void saveInstance​(java.io.FileWriter saveFile)
      Save an instance of the class implementing Savable to a text file.

      • saveInstance

        void saveInstance​(java.io.FileWriter saveFile)
           throws java.io.IOException
        Save an instance of the class implementing Savable to a text file. Note this method should not close the FileWriter it takes as an argument.
        Parameters:
        saveFile - FileWriter used to write to text file.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - due to FileWriter
